Farticleshow%2F108396778.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kate%20Middleton%20Apologises%2C%20Says%20She%20Edited%20Mother's%20Day%20Pic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECatherine%2C%20Princess%20of%20Wales%20on%20Monday%20apologised%20and%20admitted%20to%20editing%20an%20official%20portrait%20of%20her%20released%20by%20the%20palace%20after%20AFP%20and%20other%20agencies%20withdrew%20the%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKate%2C%2042%2C%20has%20not%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20since%20attending%20a%20Christmas%20Day%20church%20service%2C%20and%20underwent%20abdominal%20surgery%20in%20January%2C%20fuelling%20speculation%20about%20her%20health%2C%20particularly%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20Kensington%20Palace%20office%20on%20Sunday%20sought%20to%20dispel%20rumours%20by%20distributing%20an%20official%20photograph%20said%20to%20have%20been%20taken%20by%20her%20husband%20Prince%20William%20of%20her%20with%20their%20three%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20questions%20quickly%20emerged%20of%20the%20Mother's%20Day%20portrait%20of%20a%20smiling%20Kate%2C%20casually%20dressed%20and%20seated%20in%20a%20garden%20chair%2C%20surrounded%20by%20Prince%20George%2C%20Princess%20Charlotte%20and%20Prince%20Louis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscrepancies%20included%20several%20inconsistencies%2C%20such%20as%20Charlotte's%20left%20hand%20being%20misaligned%20with%20the%20sleeve%20of%20her%20cardigan%20and%20a%20missing%20part%20of%20her%20sleeve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight-year-old%20princess's%20hair%20ended%20abruptly%20on%20her%20shoulder%20while%20Kate's%20zip%20was%20lighter%20than%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAFP%2C%20Getty%2C%20the%20Associated%20Press%20(AP)%20and%20Reuters%20all%20have%20policies%20about%20distributing%20manipulated%20images%2C%20and%20pulled%20it%2C%20despite%20initially%20publishing%20the%20photograph%20provided%20by%20Kensington%20Palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritain's%20domestic%20Press%20Association%20said%20on%20Monday%20it%2C%20too%2C%20was%20withdrawing%20the%20image%2C%20noting%20%26quot%3Bthe%20absence%20of%20clarification%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20image%20from%20Kensington%20Palace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20minutes%20of%20PA%20announcing%20its%20decision%2C%20the%20palace%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20signed%20by%20%26quot%3BC%26quot%3B%20for%20Catherine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20many%20amateur%20photographers%2C%20I%20do%20occasionally%20experiment%20with%20editing%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20stated.%20%26quot%3BI%20wanted%20to%20express%20my%20apologies%20for%20any%20confusion%20the%20family%20photograph%20we%20shared%20yesterday%20caused.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELike%20many%20amateur%20photographers%2C%20I%20do%20occasionally%20experiment%20with%20editing.%20I%20wanted%20to%20express%20my%20apologies%20for%20any%20confusion%20the%20family%20photograph%20we%20shared%20yesterday%20caused.%20I%20hope%20everyone%20celebrating%20had%20a%20very%20happy%20Mother's%20Day.%20C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20The%20Prince%20and%20Princess%20of%20Wales%20(%40KensingtonRoyal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKensingtonRoyal%2Fstatus%2F1767135566645092616%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Damaging'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20commentators%20suggested%20the%20furore%20had%20cast%20fresh%20doubt%20on%20palace%20reassurances%20about%20Kate's%20health%20and%20recuperation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWilliam%2C%2041%2C%20and%20other%20senior%20royals%20are%20expected%20to%20attend%20the%20annual%20Commonwealth%20Day%20celebrations%20in%20central%20London%20later%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeter%20Hunt%2C%20a%20former%20BBC%20royal%20correspondent%2C%20said%20the%20situation%20was%20%26quot%3Bdamaging%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20family.%20%26quot%3BThey%20knew%20there%20would%20be%20intense%20interest%20in%20any%20picture%20they%20released%20of%20Kate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20challenge%20is%20that%20people%20will%20now%20question%20whether%20they%20can%20be%20trusted%20and%20believed%20when%20they%20next%20issue%20a%20health%20update.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGraham%20Smith%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Republic%20pressure%20group%20calling%20for%20an%20elected%20head%20of%20state%2C%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20quite%20simple.%20Don't%20use%20their%20own%20photos.%20It's%20PR%2C%20not%20news.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntense%20interest%20in%20Kate's%20absence%20comes%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20William%20--%20King%20Charles%20III's%20elder%20son%20--%20is%20heir%20to%20the%20throne%2C%20meaning%20she%20will%20one%20day%20be%20queen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Kensington%20Palace%2C%20she%20was%20admitted%20to%20the%20hospital%20on%20January%2016%20for%20planned%20surgery%2C%20then%20left%20on%20January%2029%2C%20to%20recuperate%20at%20home%20until%20at%20least%20Easter%20on%20March%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contentious%20photograph%2C%20published%20on%20all%20royal%20social%20media%20channels%20and%20widely%20picked%20up%20in%20Britain%20and%20across%20the%20world%2C%20was%20accompanied%20by%20a%20message%20signed%20by%20Kate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20your%20kind%20wishes%20and%20continued%20support%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months.%20Wishing%20everyone%20a%20Happy%20Mother's%20Day%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20note%20to%20clients%2C%20AFP%20said%20it%20withdrew%20the%20image%20after%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bcome%20to%20light%20that%20the%20handout%20issued%20by%20Kensington%20Palace%20today%20of%20Kate%20and%20the%20kids%20had%20been%20altered%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AP%20said%20it%20had%20retracted%20the%20image%20because%20on%20%26quo