ourt%20before%20April%2029%2C%20during%20the%20next%20hearing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20bench%20of%20Justices%20SA%20Dharmadhikari%20and%20Dev%20Narayan%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ASI%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20use%20all%20the%20methods%20and%20state-of-the-art%20equipment%20at%20their%20disposal%2C%20including%20Ground%20Penetration%20Radar%20System%20and%20carbon%20dating%20to%20ascertain%20the%20age%20of%20the%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20have%20asked%20for%20the%20right%20to%20daily%20worship%20at%20the%20site%20if%20a%20survey%20shows%20the%20existence%20of%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20order%2C%20the%20court%20said%20the%20ASI%20must%20conduct%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20scientific%20investigation%2C%20survey%20and%20excavation%20%2C%20through%20adoption%20of%20latest%20methods%2C%20techniques%20and%20modes%20of%20GPR-GPS%20survey%20of%20the%20site%20in%20question%20constituting%20the%20disputed%20Bhojshala%20Temple%20cum%20Kamal%20Maula%20Mosque%20complex%26quot%3B.%20This%20would%20include%20the%20entire%2050m%20of%20peripheral%20ring%20area%20from%20the%20boundary%20of%20the%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20detailed%20scientific%20investigation%20also%20has%20to%20be%20conducted%20through%20carbon%20dating%20of%20various%20structures%20%26quot%3Bboth%20above%20and%20beneath%20the%20ground%26quot%3B.%20The%20ASI%20also%20has%20to%20open%20locked%20or%20sealed%20rooms%2C%20halls%20and%20prepare%20a%20complete%20inventory%20of%20each%20and%20every%20artifact%2C%20idol%2C%20deity%2C%20or%20any%20structure.%20But%20this%20should%20be%20done%20without%20%26quot%3Bdestroying%2C%20defacing%2C%20destructing%20the%20original%20nature%20of%20the%20whole%20complex%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20should%20be%20conducted%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20an%20expert%20Committee%20of%20at%20least%20five%20senior-most%20officials%20of%20ASI%2C%20headed%20by%20the%20Director%20General%20or%20the%20Additional%20Director%20General%20and%20the%20report%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20within%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEfforts%20should%20be%20made%20to%20have%20a%20representation%20of%20Officers%20of%20both%20the%20contesting%20communities%20(if%20available%20of%20the%20said%20position%20%26amp%3B%20rank)%20in%20the%20said%20Expert%20Committee%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20after%20it%20receives%20the%20report%2C%20it%20will%20hear%20the%20claim%20of%20petitioner%20for%20restoration%20of%20the%20right%20to%20daily%20worship.%20The%20court%20will%20also%20hear%20the%20matter%20of%20investigation%20into%20the%20Waqf%20of%20Kamal%20Maula%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20at%20Dhar%2C%20where%20a%20temple%20complex%20dedicated%20to%20Goddess%20Saraswati%20exists%2C%20has%20long%20been%20a%20cause%20of%20friction.%20Currently%2C%20worship%20is%20allowed%20only%20on%20Vasant%20Panchami.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20year%2C%20namaz%20is%20offered%20at%20the%20Kamal%20Maula%20Masjid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20temple%20complex%20was%20part%20of%20a%20celebrated%20college%20built%20by%20king%20Bhoja%20(1000-1055%20AD)%2C%20said%20to%20be%20the%20greatest%20monarch%20of%20the%20Paramara%20dynasty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20college%20came%20to%20be%20known%20as%20Bhojshala%20(banquet%20hall)%2C%20where%20students%20came%20from%20across%20the%20country%20for%20a%20feast%20of%20knowledge.%20The%20structure%20was%20converted%20to%20a%20mosque%20during%20Muslim%20rule.%20The%20image%20of%20the%20Goddess%20Saraswati%20is%20now%20in%20a%20museum%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710156120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fevn8spk4_dhar-bhojshala_625x300_10_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-varanasis-gyanvapi-asi-to-conduct-survey-at-dhar-bhojshala-in-madhya-pradesh-5218015%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20disputed%20temple-mos