C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkate-middleton-absence-royal-family-what-we-know-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EMiddleton%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20her%20children%20%E2%80%94%20Prince%20George%2C%20Princess%20Charlotte%2C%20and%20Prince%20Louis%20%E2%80%94%20on%20Sunday%2C%20writing%20that%20the%20photo%20was%20taken%20by%20Price%20William.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKensingtonRoyal%2Fstatus%2F1766750995445387393%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1766750995445387393%257Ctwgr%255E3d44366913604516a2613a9fe83cbe83e2b35011%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.businessinsider.com%252Fkate-middleton-conspiracy-photograph-doctored-officially-out-of-control-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20viewed%20more%20than%2067%20million%20times%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiddleton%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkate-middleton-surgery-public-absence-what-to-know-2024-2%23%3A~%3Atext%3DUntil%2520Monday%252C%2520she%2520hadn%2527t%2Cphotos%2520or%2520videos%2520of%2520her.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elast%20seen%20in%20public%20on%20Christmas%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20first%20official%20photo%20of%20her%20that%20has%20since%20been%20released.%20Kensington%20Palace%20previously%20announced%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkate-middleton-king-charles-health-announcements-royal-pr-strategy-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMiddleton%20underwent%20a%20planned%20abdominal%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20inconsistencies%20in%20the%20photo%2C%20including%20blurred%20edges%20along%20body%20parts%20and%20window%20panes%2C%20have%20sparked%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkate-middleton-photo-fake-photo-agencies-kill-notification-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especulation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20photo%20was%20photoshopped%20or%20AI-generated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20photo%20editor%20who%20dissected%20the%20image%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20was%20surprised%20the%20photo%20was%20released%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20astonishing%20that%20Kensington%20Palace%20released%20it%2C%20and%20even%20more%20bewildering%20that%20the%20wires%20distributed%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patrick%20Witty.%20Witty%20was%20a%20photo%20editor%20at%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20from%202004%20to%202010%20and%20a%20deputy%20director%20of%20photography%20at%20National%20Geographic%20from%202016%20to%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWitty%20also%20shared%20a%20marked-up%20version%20of%20the%20image%2C%20in%20which%20he%20drew%20white%20circles%20around%20the%20areas%20that%20raised%20red%20flags%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20issue%20that%20I%20noticed%20was%20the%20weirdness%20around%20Charlotte's%20left%20wrist%20%E2%80%94%20a%20portion%20of%20her%20sleeve%20strangely%20disappears%2C%26quot%3B%20Witty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20glaring%20problem%20is%20with%20the%20zipper%20on%20Kate's%20jacket.%20It's%20as%20if%20that%20area%20was%20sloppily%20pasted%20and%20misaligned%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20there%20are%20%26quot%3Bover%20a%20dozen%20areas%20around%20Kate's%20head%20that%20are%20unnatural%26quot%3B%20and%20look%20%26quot%3Bas%20if%20they%20took%20the%20expression%20from%20one%20image%20and%20pasted%20it%20on%20top%20of%20this%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20latter%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20smartphone%20camera%20settings%2C%20Witty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20issues%20with%20this%20photo%20could%20have%20been%20caused%20by%20Portrait%20mode%20or%20perhaps%20the%20%26quot%3BBest%20Take%26quot%3B%20mode%20on%20the%20Google%20Pixel%208%2C%26quot%3B%20Witty%20said.%20The%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.google%2Fproducts%2Fphotos%2Fhow-google-photos-best-take-works%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBest%20Take%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20feature%20automatically%20chooses%20the%20most%20flattering%20expression%20for%20each%20person%20in%20a%20group%20photo%20and%20merges%20them%20into%20one%20image%2C%20Witty%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWitty%20said%20the%20background%20of%20the%20photo%2C%20which%20appears%20blurry%20and%20pixelated%2C%20could%20be%20the%20result%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportrait-mode-photos-tips-tricks-google-2017-11%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFor%2520the%2520unfamiliar%252C%2520portrait%2520mode%2Cwith%2520a%2520high%252Dend%2520DSLR.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ephone%20camera%20blurring%20the%20background%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20the%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20shared%20on%20Kensington%20Palace's%20X%20account%20on%20Monday%20morning%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKensingtonRoyal%2Fstatus%2F1767135566645092616%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMiddleton%20said%20her%20own%20photo%20editing%20was%20to%20blame%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20many%20amateur%20photographers%2C%20I%20do%20occasionally%20experiment%20with%20editing.%20I%20wanted%20to%20express%20my%20apologies%20for%20any%20confusion%20the%20family%20photograph%20we%20shared%20yesterday%20caused.%20I%20hope%20everyone%20celebrating%20had%20a%20very%20happy%20Mother's%20Day%2C%26quot%3B%20Middleton%20wrote%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReuters%2C%20Agence%20France-Presse%2C%20and%20the%20Associated%20Press%20all%20issued%20kill%20notifications%20to%20media%20outlets%20over%20the%20image.%20While%20the%20move%20has%20further%20stoked%20the%20speculation%20over%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20image%2C%20the%20move%20is%20not%20unhead%20of%20for%20agencies%2C%20Vivek%20Prakash%2C%20the%20APAC%20managing%20director%20for%20Getty%20Images