d%20it%20was%20all%20a%20scheme%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20replicate%20her%20daughter's%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaveri's%20post%20soon%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20social%20media%20users%20and%20numerous%20users%20shared%20similar%20encounters%20in%20the%20comment%20section.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20user%20shared%2C%20%26quot%3BOmg%20this%20happened%20to%20a%20friend%20back%20in%20Assam.%20Got%20a%20call%20late%20night%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bcop%26quot%3B%20who%20asked%20if%20he%20has%20P's%20dad%2C%20P%20who%20studies%20here%20and%20lives%20at%20this%20address%20in%20PG%20(across%20the%20country).%20And%20then%20told%20him%20she's%20been%20arrested%20for%20possession%20of%20drugs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20similar%20thing%20happened%20with%20my%20mum.%20Though%20my%20brother%20lives%20out%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20tone%20in%20which%20the%20self-proclaimed%20ASI%20threatened%20my%20mother%20about%20his%20whereabouts%2C%20she%20was%20really%20scared.%20It%20was%20a%20WhatsApp%20call%20and%20the%20DP%20had%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20police%20uniform%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20user%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20prevent%20this%20kind%20of%20scam%2C%20some%20people%20started%20using%20passwords%20that%20only%20their%20family%20members%20would%20know%2C%20the%20person%20with%20AI%20voice%20won't%20know%20this%2C%20I%20removed%20my%20videos%2C%20and%20audio%20from%20the%20internet%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUff%20this%20is%20very%20scary.%20I'm%20assuming%20they%20also%20know%20when%20your%20daughter%20is%20not%20actually%20with%20you.%20How%20scary%20is%20that!%20They%20know%20your%20number%2C%20your%20name%2C%20your%20daughter's%20name%2C%20and%20some%20possible%20info%20about%20her%20whereabouts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fourth%20user%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20most%20concerning%20part%20is%20your%20daughter's%20recorded%20voice.%20Needless%20to%20say%20the%20scammer%20used%20AI%20tools%20but%20getting%20access%20to%20voice%20samples%20is%20something%20that%20could%20give%20sleepless%20nights%20to%20every%20parent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20fifth%20user%20commented.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710153360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fcrtv8aro_call-generic_625x300_11_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-ai-scam-a-fake-cop-spoke-to-woman-said-her-daughter-was-arrested-5217847%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kaveri%20said%20it%20was%20all%20a%20scheme%20using%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20replicate%20her%20daughter's%20voice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-ai-scam-a-fake-cop-spoke-to-woman-said-her-daughter-was-arrested-5217847%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-ai-scam-a-fake-cop-spoke-to-woman-said-her-daughter-was-arrested-5217847%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fnew-ai-scam-a-fake-cop-spoke-to-woman-said-her-daughter-was-arrested-5217847%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20passes%20law%20granting%20Communist%20Party%20more%20control%20over%20cabinet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710153148000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108394327%2Cimgsize-438217.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-passes-law-granting-communist-party-more-control-over-cabinet%2Farticleshow%2F108394087.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108394087.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EChina's%20parliament%20has%20approved%20changes%20to%20a%20law%20that%20will%20give%20the%20Communist%20Party%20mor