0typical%20stereotypes%20associated%20with%20the%20country.%20Szymon%20Kopec%2C%20a%20product%20director%20of%20the%20global%20caller%20ID%20app%2C%20was%20travelling%20with%20his%20mother%20for%20a%20week-long%20trip.%20He%20stated%20that%20it%20was%20her%20first%20trip%20out%20of%20Europe%20and%20she%20does%20not%20speak%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mundanests%20of%20things%20were%20an%20attraction%20-%20especially%20taxi%20rides%20and%20grocery%20shopping.%20She%20came%20with%20a%20mission%20to%20buy%20'curry%20spice'%20for%20my%20sister%20and%20couldn't%20believe%20there's%20more%20than%20one%20type.%20She%20took%20approximately%20a%20billion%20photos%20of%20weeds%20and%20plants%20in%20the%20most%20random%20places%20-%20she%20was%20a%20gardener%20before%20retiring%20and%20was%20at%20awe%20with%20the%20vegetation%20here%2C%20with%20what%20in%20Europe%20are%20an%20indoor%20plants%20requiring%20tonnes%20of%20maintenance%20just%20growing%20our%20in%20the%20wild%20next%20to%20some%20highway%20toilet%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kopec%20wrote%20while%20describing%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20India%20is%20portrayed%20as%20a%20land%20with%20slums%20and%20overcrowded%20trains.%20However%2C%20a%20trip%20on%20the%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20Train%20changed%20the%20entire%20picture.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%20image%20of%20India%20in%20Poland%20is%20mostly%20portraying%20slums%20and%20overcrowded%20trains%20with%20people%20hanging%20on%20rooftops.%20Taking%20a%20perfectly%20on-time%20Vande%20Bharat%20debunked%20some%20stereotypes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI've%20traveled%20with%20my%20mom%20in%20India%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20for%20a%20week%20and%20here's%20what%20she%20loved%20about%20it%20%E2%AC%87%EF%B8%8F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20was%20her%20first%20time%20out%20of%20Europe%20and%20she%20doesn't%20speak%20English.%20She's%20heard%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20country%20from%20me%2C%20read%20in%20Polish%20media%2C%20yet%20everything%20around%20here%20was%20shocking.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20The%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FY0Du0GSBwR%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FY0Du0GSBwR%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Szymon%20Kope%C4%87%20(%40szymonkopec)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fszymonkopec%2Fstatus%2F1766386263777784290%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%209%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20same%20goes%20for%20Dehli%20and%20its%20green%2C%20beautifully%20maintained%20neighbourhoods.%20%C2%A0Tech%20ecosystem%20blew%20her%20mind.%20In%20Poland%20we're%20so%20far%20behind%20in%20that%20regard%2C%20while%20here%20I've%20shown%20her%20that%20there's%20an%20app%20for%20literally%20anything%20she%20imagines%20%2B%206%20alternatives%20from%20competitors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kopec%20added%20that%20they%20are%20not%20entirely%20taught%20about%20India's%20history.%20%26quot%3BVisiting%20Taj%20Mahal%20or%20forts%20in%20Jaipur%20was%20a%20eye-opening%20to%20what%20the%20country%20was%20for%20centuries%2C%20pre%20colonisation.%26quot%3B%20The%20executive%20concluded%20by%20saying%20that%20his%20mother%20was%20overjoyed%20by%20the%20hospitality%20and%20what%20%26quot%3Bshe%20loved%20the%20most%20were%20the%20people.%26quot%3B%20He%20shared%20a%20photo%20with%20his%20mother%20from%20the%20trip%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThough%20she%20couldn't%20communicate%20with%20them%2C%20seeing%20joy%20all%20around%20and%20having%20these%20little%20interactions%20was%20precious%2C%20as%20everyone%20was%20beyond%20kind%20and%20we've%20had%200%20less-than-positive%20experiences.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Truecaller%20executive%20added%20that%20even%20though%20his%20mother%20is%20back%20home%2C%20%26quot%3Bshe%20hasn't%20stopped%20pitching%20India%20as%20an%20i