acy%20without%20affecting%20or%20influencing%20anyone%20else%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20moment%20an%20accused%20tries%20to%20circulate%20or%20distribute%20or%20publicly%20exhibit%20obscene%20photos%20and%20videos%2C%20then%20the%20ingredients%20of%20the%20offence%20starts%20kicking%20in...%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20reasoned%20that%20to%20qualify%20as%20an%20offence%20under%20POCSO%2C%20and%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20the%20accused%20had%20to%20have%20created%2C%20published%2C%20and%20transmitted%20the%20material.%20And%20wth%20relation%20to%20the%20IT%20Act%2C%20it%20said%20the%20relevant%20section%20did%20not%20cover%20cases%20where%20an%20individual%20only%20downloaded%20and%20watched%20content%2C%20without%20doing%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20therefore%20quashed%20proceedings%20against%20a%2028-year-old%20man%20who%20had%20been%20charged%20with%20downloading%20child%20pornographic%20content%20to%20his%20mobile%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadras-high-court-expresses-concern-over-gen-z-grappling-with-pornography-4850189%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMadras%20High%20Court's%20Concern%20Over%20Gen-Z%20%26quot%3BGrappling%26quot%3B%20With%20Porn%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20all%20legal%20action%20against%20the%20accused%20was%20dropped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20High%20Court%20did%2C%20however%2C%20complain%20about%20children%20today%20%26quot%3Bgrappling%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20watching%20pornography%2C%20declaring%20it%20could%20have%20negative%20consequences%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20declaring%20the%20accused%20to%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bafflicted%20with%20this%20(watching%20pornography)%20addiction%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20advised%20counselling%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%20and%20happy%20future%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E