ip%20to%20the%20BJP's%20'Mission%20400'%20and%20its%20efforts%20to%20expand%20its%20footprint%20in%20Southern%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOld%20Friends%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20and%20the%20BJP%20share%20an%20old%20relationship.%20The%20party%20first%20joined%20the%20NDA%20in%201996%20but%20left%20after%20the%202004%20polls.%20It%20returned%20to%20the%20fold%20almost%20a%20decade%20later%20for%20the%202014%20general%20elections%2C%20before%20parting%20ways%20in%202018%20again%20over%20the%20issue%20of%20grant%20of%20special%20status%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20after%20the%20bifurcation%20of%20Telangana.%20The%20latest%20return%20marks%20the%20TDP's%20third%20one%20after%20a%20bitter%20break-up%20in%20the%20past%20-%20politics%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20an%20art%20of%20forgetting%20and%20forgiving.%20It%20also%20joins%20the%20ranks%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20(JD-U)%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20in%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20has%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20thrice%20-%20twice%20in%20united%20Andhra%20and%20once%20after%20its%20bifurcation.%20On%20September%201%2C%201995%2C%20he%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20following%20a%20successful%20coup%20against%20the%20leadership%20of%20N.T.%20Rama%20Rao.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20fought%20the%201999%20and%202014%20elections%20together%20and%20formed%20a%20coalition%20government%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhenever%20Naidu%20has%20won%20elections%20in%20the%20state%2C%20it%20has%20been%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20BJP%2C%20thus%2C%20is%20sort%20of%20a%20good%20omen%20for%20the%20party%2C%20notwithstanding%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20alliance%20did%20lose%20badly%20in%202004%20to%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Pragmatic%20Shift%20Away%20From%20INDIA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20true%20that%20Naidu%20until%20a%20few%20months%20back%20had%20been%20exploring%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20was%20apparently%20keen%20to%20join%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%20According%20to%20reports%2C%20he%20had%20even%20backed%20Revanth%20Reddy's%20campaign%20in%20Telangana.%20However%2C%20the%20Congress's%20shock%20loss%20in%20three%20Hindi%20heartland%20states%20last%20year%20seems%20to%20have%20changed%20his%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVote%20Share%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPARTY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1999%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2004%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2009%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2014%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2019%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E40.6%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E38.6%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E36.6%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.8%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.2%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETDP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E43.9%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E37.6%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E28.1%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E44.9%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E39.7%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.9%25%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%