0the%20BJP's%20relatively%20thinner%20popularity%20South%20of%20Vindhyas%2C%20except%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20been%20facing%20a%20problem%20of%20plenty%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20After%20the%20TDP's%20exit%20in%202018%2C%20it%20had%20found%20a%20new%20partner%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frusted-cycle-jagan-mohan-reddys-swipe-at-chandrababu-naidu-5212824%5C%22%3EJagan%20Reddy's%20Yuvajana%20Sramika%20Rythu%20Congress%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20(YSRCP).%20The%20party%2C%20deemed%20the%20'real%20Congress'%20in%20Andhra%20(as%20the%20numbers%20exhibit)%2C%20has%20backed%20the%20BJP%20on%20important%20and%20even%20contentious%20bills%20in%20Parliament%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20lacked%20a%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20An%20Alliance%20With%20YSRCP%20Couldn't%20Be%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20YSRCP%20could%20not%20materialise%20due%20to%20fears%20of%20loss%20of%20the%20support%20of%20minorities%2C%20who%20account%20for%2011%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%20As%20many%20as%2054%25%20of%20them%20had%20backed%20the%20YSRCP%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections.%20With%20Jagan's%20sister%20Sharmila%20joining%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20YSRCP's%20entry%20into%20the%20NDA%20could%20have%20led%20to%20a%20shift%20of%20the%20minority%20vote%20towards%20the%20Congress.%20Jagan%2C%20who%20is%20already%20fighting%20a%20tough%20battle%20in%20his%20backyard%2C%20didn't%20want%20to%20take%20that%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20still%20needed%20an%20official%20partnership%20to%20shore%20up%20its%20numbers%20in%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20and%20that%20is%20perhaps%20the%20reason%20it%20decided%20to%20strike%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20TDP-despite%20Naidu%20having%20called%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20a%20terrorist%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20Takes%20A%20Long%20View%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20sees%20an%20opportunity%20to%20grow%20in%20Andhra%20with%20this%20move.%20Naidu%20is%2073%2C%20and%20this%20could%20be%20his%20last%20election.%20As%20with%20many%20regional%20parties%2C%20observers%20feel%20his%20son%20Lokesh%20lacks%20the%20charisma%20to%20lead%20after%20Naidu%20hangs%20up%20his%20boots.%20Just%20like%20in%20Odisha%20(post-Naveen%20era)%20and%20Bihar%20(post-Nitish%20era)%2C%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20have%20a%20long-term%20plan%20for%20Andhra%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndhra%20faces%20simultaneous%20polls%20like%20Odisha%2C%20and%20the%20NDA's%20success%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20depends%20on%20how%20the%20TDP%20performs%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20The%20state%20is%20witnessing%20a%20tight%20battle%20currently%20as%20Jagan%20turns%20his%20focus%20on%20the%20%3Cem%3Elaabharthi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(beneficiary)%20factor%20and%20young%20faces%20to%20counter%20anti-incumbency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%C2%A0%C2%A0is%20relying%20on%20the%20exodus%20of%20leaders%20from%20Jagan's%20camp%2C%20the%20'sympathy%20factor'%20after%20his%20arrest%20last%20year%2C%20the%20addition%20of%20the%20Kapu%20samaj%20votes%20due%20to%20the%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20factor%2C%20and%20Jagan's%20failure%20at%20achieving%20a%20special%20category%20status%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Ironically%2C%20the%20last%20bit%20was%20the%20same%20weapon%20Jagan%20had%20to%20unseat%20Naidu%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENaidu%20In%20A%20Tight%20Spot%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20TDP%20does%20well%2C%20it%20will%20add%20a%20few%20seats%20to%20the%20NDA's%20kitty%20and%20help%20its%20Mission%20400.%20Its%20failure%20to%20do%20so%20could%20lead%20to%20an%20existential%20crisis%20for%20the%20party%20and%20open%20up%20a%20gap-which%2C%20party%20strategists%20hope%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20be%20able%20to%20fill.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Naidu%2C%20this%20is%20a%20do-or-die%20battle%20and%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20leave%20anything%20to%20chance.%20With%20BJP%20on%20its%20side%2C%20the%20TDP%20hopes%20to%20give%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20formidable%20Jagan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710148200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F07rsj664_bjp-tdp-alliance_640x480_08_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-andhras-tdp-bjp-alliance-stakes-are-higher-for-naidu-5217372%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20BJP%20on%20its%20side%2C%20the%20TDP%20hopes%20to%20give%20a%20tough%20fight%20to%20the%20formidable%20Jagan%20Reddy.%20However%2C%20a%20not-so-good%20performance%20can%20lead%20to%20an%20existential%20crisis%20for%20Naidu's%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-andhras-tdp-bjp-alliance-stakes-are-higher-for-naidu-5217372%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-andhras-tdp-bjp-alliance-stakes-are-higher-for-naidu-5217372%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fin-andhras-tdp-bjp-alliance-stakes-are-higher-for-naidu-5217372%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20dies%20of%20cardiac%20arrest%20after%20witnessing%20hubby's%20murder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710148090000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108390889%2Cimgsize-20978.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Famaravati%2F