20in%20recent%20years%20has%20affected%20traditional%20retailers%2C%20particularly%20those%20like%20The%20Body%20Shop%2C%20which%20predominantly%20operated%20out%20of%20malls%20and%20were%20aimed%20at%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK-based%20cosmetics%20company%2C%20founded%20in%201976%20by%20human%20rights%20activist%20and%20environmental%20campaigner%20Anita%20Roddick%2C%20is%20known%20for%20products%20it%20markets%20as%20natural%2C%20sustainable%2C%20ethical%20and%20cruelty-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20companies%20to%20prohibit%20testing%20on%20animals%20for%20many%20of%20its%20products%2C%20according%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20in%202019%2C%20it%20was%20certified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BB%20Corp%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20designation%20given%20to%20companies%20that%20meet%20certain%20transparency%20and%20environmental%20conscientiousness%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202023%2C%20it%20had%20expanded%20to%20more%20than%202%2C500%20retail%20locations%20in%20over%2080%20countries%20and%20was%20available%20to%20purchase%20online%20in%20more%20than%2060%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20inception%2C%20The%20Body%20Shop%20has%20changed%20hands%20several%20times.%20It%20was%20purchased%20by%20cosmetics%20giant%20L'Oreal%20in%202006%20for%20more%20than%20a%20billion%20dollars%20and%20later%20sold%20to%20Brazilian%20company%20Natura%20in%202017%20for%20another%20billion%20dollars%2C%20reported%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20brand%20fell%20into%20hard%20times%20and%20has%20been%20ailing%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20early%202023%20report%2C%20Natura%20noted%20that%20The%20Body%20Shop%20was%20%26quot%3B(facing)%20headwinds%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20year-over-year%20decline%20of%2013.5%20per%20cent%20in%202022%2C%20a%20year%20the%20company%20said%20%26quot%3Bwas%20far%20from%20easy%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20brand.%20Its%20direct-to-consumer%20channels%2C%20which%20had%2