ve%20been%20taken%20to%20control%20the%20water%20%26quot%3Bmafia%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%2030-40%20years%20we%20had%20not%20seen%20such%20drought%3B%20though%20there%20was%20drought%20earlier%20we%20had%20never%20declared%20such%20a%20large%20number%20of%20taluks%20as%20drought-affected%2C%26quot%3B%20Shivakumar%20told%20reporters%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivakumar%2C%20also%20in-charge%20of%20Bengaluru%20development%2C%20said%20wherever%20Cauvery%20river%20water%20has%20to%20be%20supplied%20in%20the%20city%2C%20it%20is%20being%20done%2C%20but%20out%20of%2013%2C900-odd%20borewells%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20about%206%2C900%20have%20become%20defunct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20to%20control%20the%20situation%2C%20we%20have%20arranged%20for%20tankers%20to%20supply%20water.%20Bruhat%20Bengaluru%20Mahanagara%20Palike%20(BBMP)%20and%20Bangalore%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%20(BWSSB)%20are%20making%20all%20efforts%20in%20this%20regard%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20has%20declared%20drought%20in%20223%20out%20of%20240%20taluks%2C%20out%20of%20which%20196%20are%20categorised%20as%20severely%20drought%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20that%20the%20opposition%20(BJP-JD(S)%20combine)%20was%20trying%20to%20indulge%20in%20politics%20over%20the%20issue%2C%20Shivakumar%20said%20the%20administration%20has%20on%20its%20part%20made%20efforts%20to%20control%20the%20water%20%26quot%3Bmafia%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20provide%20water%20by%20taking%20it%20from%20private%20borewells%2C%20and%20also%20rates%20have%20been%20fixed%20based%20on%20distance%20travelled%20by%20the%20water%20tankers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20separate%20online%20system%20has%20been%20brought%20in%20for%20this%20and%20officials%20have%20been%20appointed%20to%20oversee%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20next%20two%20months%20are%20%26quot%3Bvery%20much%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Shivakumar%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20Water%20Resources%20Minister%2C%20said%20priority%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20wastage%20of%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(By%20implementing)%20Cauvery%20fifth%20stage%20(project)%20--%20we%20will%20make%20all%20efforts%20to%20provide%20Cauvery%20water%20to%20110%20villages%20(around%20Bengaluru)%20at%20the%20earliest%20by%20May%20last%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20control%20the%20water%20%26quot%3Bmafia%26quot%3B%2C%20more%20than%201%2C500%20private%20water%20tankers%20have%20registered%20so%20far%20and%20time%20has%20been%20extended%20for%20others%20also%20to%20register%20till%20March%2015%2C%20Shivakumar%20further%20said.%20Police%2C%20Regional%20Transport%20Office%20(RTO)%2C%20BBMP%20and%20BWSSB%20will%20monitor%20it%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20board%20with%20registration%20number%20on%20tankers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOperating%20illegally%20and%20charging%20exorbitantly%20Rs%205%2C000%20or%206%2C000%20(per%20tanker%20of%20water)%2C%20such%20things%20are%20going%20on.%20To%20control%2C%20its%20price%20has%20been%20fixed%20based%20on%20the%20distance%20travelled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ramanagara%2C%20Magadi%2C%20Doddaballapura%2C%20Hoskote%20and%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20there%20are%20irrigation%20borewells%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20have%20taken%20a%20count%20of%20them%2C%20to%20draw%20water%20from%20there%20if%20an%20emergency%20situation%20arises.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710143400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fc694cod8_dk-shivakumar_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-seen-such-drought