Take%20On%20Pacer's%20Remarks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricket%20team%20head%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggested%20that%20the%20domestic%20cricket%20scheduling%20should%20go%20through%20an%20'all-round%20review'%20after%20players%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shardul%20Thakur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63779-shardul-narendra-thakur-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShardul%20Thakur%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20R%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sai%20Kishore%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107511-ravisrinivasan-sai-kishore-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESai%20Kishore%3C%2Fa%3E%20expressed%20their%20concerns.%20Shardul%20said%20that%20players%20need%20more%20breaks%20between%20the%20matches%20in%20order%20to%20avoid%20injury%20and%20his%20sentiments%20were%20echoed%20by%20Sai%20Kishore.%20Following%20India's%20win%20over%20England%20in%20the%20fifth%20Test%20match%20in%20Dharamsala%2C%20Dravid%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20concerns%20and%20he%20said%20that%20the%20BCCI%20should%20consult%20the%20players%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20through%20the%20grind%20and%20putting%20their%20bodies%20on%20the%20line.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20heard%20the%20same%20as%20well.%20I%20saw%20some%20of%20the%20comments%20Shardul%2C%20I%20think%2C%20made.%20And%20in%20fact%20some%20of%20the%20boys%20who've%20come%20into%20the%20team%20as%20well%2C%20also%20comment%20about%20how%20tough%20the%20domestic%20schedule%20is%2C%20especially%20in%20a%20country%20like%20India%20with%20the%20amount%20of%20travel%20involved.%20So%20yeah%2C%20we%20need%20to%20hear%20the%20players.%20That's%20a%20very%20important%20thing%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20these%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Dravid%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20hear%20your%20players%2C%20because%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20going%20through%20the%20grind%20and%20putting%20their%20bodies%20on%20the%20line%2C%20and%20if%20there%20are%20enough%20voices%20saying%20that%2C%20then%20yeah%2C%20I%20think%20there's%20some%20need%20to%20look%20at%20it%2C%20and%20see%20how%20we%20can%20manage%20our%20schedules.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDravid%20also%20urged%20the%20BCCI%20to%20look%20into%20the%20scheduling%20of%20other%20competitions%20like%20Duleep%20Trophy%20and%20Deodhar%20Trophy%20to%20manage%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20cricketers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20long%20season%20already%20in%20India.%20It's%20tough%2C%26quot%3B%20Dravid%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Ranji%20Trophy%20is%20a%20long%20season%2C%20and%20if%20you%20add%20a%20Duleep%20and%20a%20Deodhar%20on%20top%20of%20that...Last%20year%2C%20if%20I'm%20not%20mistaken%2C%20the%20Duleep%20started%20in%20June%2C%20it%20was%20just%20a%20month%20after%20the%20IPL%2C%20and%20your%20problem%20in%20this%20situation%20is%20your%20best%20players%2C%20the%20guys%20who%20are%20pushing%20for%20selection%20for%20India%2C%20are%20the%20ones%20that%20end%20up%20playing%20the%20most%20cricket.%20Because%20they%20keep%20getting%20selected%20at%20the%20next%20level%2C%20more%20and%20more%2C%20and%20their%20teams%20are%20the%20ones%20probably%20who%20are%20playing%20the%20semi-finals%20and%20the%20finals%2C%20or%20that%20kind%20of%20situation.%20They%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20end%20up%20playing%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%2C%20and%20you%20also%20want%20them%20to%20be%20playing%20for%20India%2C%20and%20India%20A%20tours%2C%20and%20so%20it%20can%20get%20quite%20tough%20on%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20boys%2C%20and%20maybe%20we%20need%20to%20hear%20them%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20we%20need%20to%20re-look%20and%20see%20whether%20some%20of%20the%20tournaments%20that%20we%20are%20conducting%20are%20necessary%20in%20this%20day%20and%20age%20or%20if%20they%20are%20not%20necessary.%20There%