0Catalyst%20for%20Female%20Labour%20Force%20Participation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10173957%2Fbelle-maluf-MxF6x11ICWs-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20years%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20urban%20employment%20landscape%20has%20witnessed%20a%20new%20entrant%20in%20the%20form%20of%20Urban%20Employment%20Programmes%20(UEPs)%2C%20currently%20implemented%20across%20nine%20Indian%20states.%20The%20latest%20offering%20%E2%80%93%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Rozgar%20Yojna%20(IRGY)%20%E2%80%93%20was%20launched%20in%202022%20with%20an%20ambitious%20Rs%20800-crore%20budget%2C%20to%20address%20issues%20of%20urban%20poverty%2C%20inflation%20and%20joblessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20these%20problems%20is%20large%2C%20and%20gendered.%20India%E2%80%99s%20unemployment%20rate%20remains%20around%208-9%25%2C%20yet%20the%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS)%20reveals%20that%20only%2021.9%25%20of%20women%20aged%2015%20and%20above%20in%20urban%20areas%20participate%20in%20the%20workforce%2C%20with%20a%20significant%2091%25%20employed%20in%20the%20informal%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20UEPs%20across%20India%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1003041%2Fhow-urban-employment-schemes-can-offer-social-security-to-the-poor-and-empower-women%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20note%20the%20predominance%20of%20women%20workers%2C%20and%20our%20research%20in%20Rajasthan%20suggests%20that%20over%2090%25%20of%20IRGY%20beneficiaries%20are%20women.%20These%20metrics%20indicate%20a%20positive%20movement%20towards%20gender%20inclusivity%20and%20empowerment.%20A%20review%20of%20UEPs%20across%20India%20and%20insights%20from%20the%20field%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Odisha%20help%20us%20understand%20what%20draws%20women%20to%20these%20programmes%20and%20identify%20best%20practices%20and%20learnings%20that%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20sustained%20increase%20female%20labour%20force%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20contexts%20and%20household%20dynamics%20are%20key%20determinants%20for%20lower%20female%20labour%20force%20participation.%20UEPs%20provides%20many%20women%20a%20pathway%20to%20enter%20the%20labour%20market%2C%20hitherto%20unavailable%20due%20to%20limited%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20unpaid%20care%20responsibilities%2C%20and%20other%20limitations%20placed%20by%20households%2C%20such%20as%20distance%20to%20work%2C%20work%20timings%2C%20and%20the%20concerns%20about%20safety%20outside%20the%20home%20and%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUEPs%20address%20these%20issues%20by%20offering%20a%20structured%20and%20supportive%20environment%20for%20women%20to%20enter%20the%20formal%20labour%20market.%20For%20informal%20workers%20such%20as%20home-based%20workers%2C%20UEPs%20substitute%20exploitative%20labour%20and%20wages%20(often%20as%20low%20as%20Rs.%2050%20a%20day)%20with%20a%20guaranteed%20minimum%20wage.%20Domestic%20workers%20benefit%20from%20a%20single%20worksite%2C%20reducing%20time%20and%20cost%20spent%20on%20commuting%2C%20and%20facilitating%20better%20management%20of%20household%20tasks.%20Similarly%2C%20casual%20workers%2C%20such%20as%20those%20in%20construction%2C%20find%20UEPs%20safer%20and%20easier%20to%20access%2C%20even%20if%20wages%20may%20be%20slightly%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22In%20Charts%3A%20How%20Women%20Continue%20to%20Shoulder%20the%20Burden%20of%20Unpaid%20Work%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fin-charts-how-women-continue-to-shoulder-the-burden-of-unpaid-work%5C%22%3EIn%20Charts%3A%20How%20Women%20Continue%20to%20Shoulder%20the%20Burden%20of%20Unpaid%20Work%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUEPs%20also%20offer%20a%20sense%20of%20safety%20for%20women%2C%20as%20many%20reported%20feeling%20safer%20due%20to%20the%20presence%20of%20other%20woman%20at%20the%20worksite.%20Women%20also%20found%20camaraderie%20and%20built%20stronger%20social%20networks%20at%20worksites.%20Ironically%2C%20these%20workspaces%20became%20unexpected%20spaces%20of%20leisure%20granting%20women%20a%20break%20from%20relentless%20household%20responsibilities.%20This%20support%20extended%20beyond%20the%20workday%2C%20with%20women%20forging%20friendships%20that%20helped%20navigate%20personal%20lives%20and%20crises.%20The%20programme%20also%20granted%20women%20a%20degree%20of%20autonomy%20by%20empowering%20them%20with%20financial%20resources%20and%20a%20role%20in%20household%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20social%20contexts%20that%20make%20UEPs%20attractive.%20Informal%20work%20is%20layered%20with%20precarities%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20the%20task%20of%20finding%20work%20frequently.%20UEPs%20guarantee%20work%20(up%20to%20125%20days%20in%20Rajasthan)%20and%20often%20back%20this%20promise%20with%20unemployment%20allowances.%20UEPs%20also%20offer%20multiple%20avenues%20for%20workers%20to%20register%20for%20work%2C%20including%20camps%20organised%20by%20Urban%20Local%20Bodies%20and%20Civil%20Society%20Organisations%2C%20online%20registration%2C%20and%20support%20centres%20like%20e-mitra.%20The%20diversity%20of%20options%20and%20quick%20enrolment%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20barriers%20to%20entry%20that%20women%20face%20when%20applying%20for%20other%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20despite%20these%20benefits%2C%20UEPs%2C%20face%20criticism%20for%20offering%20lower-than-market%20wages%2C%20and%20for%20excessive%20focus%20on%20manual%20labour%20and%20for%20the%20quality%20of%20employment.%20Considering%20these%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%2C%20we%20recommend%20several%20improvements%20for%20UEPs%20to%20elevate%20female%20labour%20force%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBroaden%20Eligibility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Access%20to%20UEPs%20in%20India%20are%20mostly%20restricted%20to%20residents.%20Not%20only%20does%20this%20leave%20out%20migrant%20women%2C%20who%20are%20often%20more%20vulnerable%2C%20but%20also%20long-term%20residents%20who%20may%20be%20considered%20migrants%20%E2%80%98on%20paper%E2%80%99%20and%20unable%20to%20meet%20the%20eligibility%20criteria%2C%20enforced%20through%20requirements%20such%20as%20Aadhaar%2C%20ration%20cards%2C%20or%20voter%20ID%20cards.%20UEPs%20must%20consider%20non-local%20identification%2C%20such%20as%20Aadhaar%2C%20and%20ID%20cards%20generated%20through%20worker%20organisations%20or%20unions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOffer%20Flexible%20Work%20Options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Recognising%20the%20burden%20of%20household%20work%2C%20UEPs%20can%20offer%20flexible%20work%20options%2C%20allowing%20women%20to%20choose%20shorter%20daily%20shifts%20of%20three%20to%20four%20hours%2C%20or%20condensed%20workweeks%20of%20two%20to%20three%20days.%20Similar%20employment%20programmes%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1057%2F9781137313997_4%5C%22%3EArgentina%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20offered%20such%20options.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levyinstitute.org%2Fpubs%2Fwp_519.pdf%5C%22%3EArgentina%E2%80%99s%20Plan%20Jefes%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20effective%2C%20with%20nearly%2070%25%20of%20beneficiaries%20being%20women.%20Studies%20show%20improved%20access%20to%20social%20services%2C%20reduced%20school%20dropout%20rates%2C%20and%20lower%20levels%20of%20abuse%20and%20crime.%20Women%20also%20report%20gaining%20additional%20skills%2C%20improving%20their%20chances%20of%20obtaining%20other%20paid%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Despite%20Talk%20of%20Diversity%2C%20Women%20Still%20a%20Minority%20in%20Indian%20Boardrooms%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fdespite-talk-of-diversity-women-still-a-minority-in-indian-boardrooms%5C%22%3EDespite%20Talk%20of%20Diversity%2C%20Women%20Still%20a%20Minority%20in%20Indian%20Boardrooms%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExpand%20the%20Scope%20of%20Work%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20UEPs%20must%20target%20an%20expanded%20list%20of%20work%2C%20such%20as%20building%20and%20managing%20economic%20and%20social%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20can%20include%20childcare%20facilities%20(creches)%2C%20canteens%2C%20and%20multi-purpose%20centres%20(MPCCs)%20where%20women%20can%20collectivise%2C%20work%2C%20and%20rest.%20Women%20can%20also%20be%20granted%20work%20in%20community%20kitchens%2C%20and%20educational%20institutions%2C%20as%20well%20as%20public%20institutions%20such%20as%20Anganwaadis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImprove%20Accessibility%20and%20Mobility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20UEPs%20should%20provide%20work%20closer%20to%20home%20and%20within%20a%201-2%20km%20radius%20to%20minimise%20transit%20time%20and%20cost.%20Alternatively%2C%20a%20transportation%20allowance%20(as%20practiced%20in%20Kerala)%20or%20free-to-use%20public%20transport%20can%20benefit%20women%20workers%20and%20enhance%20their%20mobility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrioritise%20Safety%20and%20Comfort%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Many%20women%20prefer%20UEPs%20because%20they%20provide%20safe%20spaces%20for%20decent%20work.%20Workplace%20amenities%20must%20include%20toilets%2C%20resting%20spaces%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20and%20childcare%20facilities.%20This%20can%20set%20a%20positive%20benchmark%20for%20private%20markets%20as%20well%20and%20increase%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWages%20and%20Skilling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Typically%2C%20UEPs%20are%20aligned%20to%20minimum%20state%20wages.%20However%2C%20states%20must%20consider%20introducing%20the%20concept%20of%20living%20wages%2C%20which%20broadens%20the%20discussion%20on%20wages%20to%20include%20skill%20levels%2C%20and%20account%20for%20input%20factors%20such%20as%20the%20nature%20and%20location%20of%20work.%20A%20model%20such%20as%20this%20will%20additionally%20build%20a%20component%20of%20apprenticeship%2C%20allowing%20new%20and%20unskilled%20workers%20to%20learn%20from%20experienced%20workers%20and%20eventually%20find%20e%20permanent%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20UEPs%20are%20a%20vital%20lifeline%20for%20many%20women%20in%20urban%20India%2C%20high%20uptake%20should%20not%20be%20the%20end%20goal.%20UEPs%20must%20go%20beyond%20being%20safety%20nets%2C%20to%20imbibe%20not%20just%20protective%20and%20preventive%20measures%2C%20but%20transformative%20measures%20that%20address%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation.%20This%20will%20need%20UEPs%20to%20adopt%20a%20more%20innovative%20approach%2C%20offering%20better%20wages%2C%20an%20expansive%20set%20of%20contextualised%20works%2C%20greater%20access%2C%20as%20well%20as%20safety%20and%20dignity.%20The%20true%20measure%20of%20success%20lies%20in%20building%20upon%20this%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVrashali%20Khandelwal%20is%20a%20Consultant%20at%20Indian%20Institute%20for%20Human%20Settlements%20(IIHS)%20and%20her%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Ework%20revolves%20around%20issues%20of%20informality%20and%20social%20protection.%20Sukrit%20Nagpal%20is%20a%20researcher%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Epractitioner%20at%20IIHS%20and%20his%20work%20focuses%20on%20urban%20housing%20and%20informal%20work.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710122452000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10173957%2Fbelle-maluf-MxF6x11ICWs-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Furban-employment-programmes-a-catalyst-for-female-labour-force-participation%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Urban%20employment%20programmes%20must%20go%20beyond%20being%20safety%20nets%2C%20to%20imbibe%20not%20just%20protective%20and%20preventive%20measures%2C%20but%20transformative%20measures%20that%20address%20women%E2%80%99s%20labour%20force%20participation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Furban-employment-programmes-a-catalyst-for-female-labour-force-participation%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22News%20agencies%20recall%20post-surgery%20image%20of%20UK's%20Princess%20Kate%20Middleton%20over%20manipulation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710121189000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108378156%2Cimgsize-1030815.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fnews-agencies-recall-post-surgery-image-of-uks-princess-kate-middleton-over-manipulation%2Farticleshow%2F108378075.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108378075.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ENumerous%20prominent%20news%20outlets%20have%20withdrawn%20a%20photograph%20released%20by%20Kensington%20Palace%20featuring%20Catherine%2C%20Princess%20of%20Wales%2C%20alongside%20her%20children%2C%20amid%20concerns%20of%20potential%20digital%20manipulation.%20Photo%20distributors%2C%20including%20Reuters%2C%20the%20Associated%20Press%2C%20Getty%2C%20and%20AFP%2C%20have%20all%20retracted%20the%20Mother's%20Day%20image%20distributed%20by%20Kensington%20Palace%20last%20Sunday%2C%20citing%20suspicions%20of%20digital%20alteration.%20The%20photo%20showcased%20Kate%20Middleton%20and%20her%20three%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fnews-agencies-recall-post-surgery-image-of-uks-princess-kate-middleton-over-manipulation%2Farticleshow%2F108378075.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fnews-agencies-recall-post-surgery-image-of-uks-princess-kate-middleton-over-manipulation%2Famp_articleshow%2F108378075.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fnews-agencies-recall-post-surgery-image-of-uks-princess-kate-middleton-over-manipulation%2Famp_articleshow%2F108378075.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20an%20Alternative%20Ideology%20Is%20Important%3A%20The%20Far-Right%20Is%20Loud%2C%20Not%20the%20Silent%20Majority%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EBullying%20and%20ragging%20were%20common%20in%20Sainik%20School%20where%20I%20grew%20up.%20Masculine%20boys%20ruled%2C%20as%20was%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20entire%20training%20and%20education%20of%20the%20school.%20They%20did%20not%20necessarily%20have%20well-built%20bodies%20nor%20performed%20well%20in%20studies%2C%20drills%2C%20physical%20training%2C%20or%20shooting.%20Instead%2C%20some%20of%20them%20would%20not%20stand%20a%20chance%20in%20case%20they%20were%20even%20slapped.%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20lethargic%20rule%20breakers%20and%20often%20had%20to%20attend%20the%20punishment%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20did%20not%20have%20the%20moral%20high%20ground%2C%20yet%20they%20were%20powerful.%20They%20were%20loud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20always%20present%2C%20generating%20clamour.%20Despite%20their%20obnoxious%20demeanour%2C%20they%20always%20found%20ways%20to%20get%20away%2C%20seized%20the%20best%20opportunities.%20Cadets%20like%20me%20felt%20like%20losers.%20We%20followed%20rules%2C%20never%20bunked%20classes%2C%20or%20missed%20the%20devastating%20morning%20PT%20or%203%20am%20drill.%20But%20there%20were%20no%20prizes%20for%20us.%20Whereas%20our%20bullies%20always%20received%20rewards.%20We%20thought%20they%20would%20always%20win.%20We%20were%20hopeless%20and%20tempted%20to%20give%20up.%20We%20would%20simply%20succumb%20to%20their%20bullying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFar%E2%80%93right%20parties%2C%20much%20like%20those%20bullies%2C%20are%20loud.%20They%20yell%2C%20they%20shout%2C%20they%20bulldoze%2C%20the%20vocal%20minority%20claps%20in%20approval%2C%20and%20they%20win.%20And%20non-far-right%20parties%20and%20individuals%20often%20perceive%20them%20as%20unbeatable%2C%20thinking%20that%20bullies%20have%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-far-right-is-not-the-people%5C%22%3Epeople%E2%80%99s%20support.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20psychology%20is%20demoralised%2C%20defeated.%20This%20is%20not%20to%20claim%20moral%20or%20intellectual%20superiority%2C%20nor%20do%20we%20seek%20to%20dismiss%20far%E2%80%93right%20as%20street%20goons.%20That%20would%20be%20a%20self-defeating%20trope.%20But%20the%20goodness%20in%20us%20makes%20us%20play%20it%20safe%2C%20becoming%20cautious%20citizens%2C%20effectively%20rendering%20us%20inactive%20and%20hesitant%20to%20take%20initiatives%20that%20might%20involve%20even%20the%20slightest%20possibility%20of%20risk.%20We%20avoid%20trouble%2C%20shy%20away%20from%20confrontation.%20And%20should%20we%2C%20really%3F%20It%20drains%20us%2C%20it%20is%20an%20exhausting%20and%20persistent%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20liberal%20political%20commentators%20have%20been%20quick%20to%20attribute%20extremist%20acts%20of%20religious%20vandalism%20to%20fringe%20elements.%20They%20dismissed%20them%20as%20outside%20the%20mainstream%20political%20discourse.%20However%2C%20over%20the%20past%20decade%20under%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20rule%2C%20we%20have%20witnessed%20the%20transformation%20of%20once-termed%20%E2%80%9Cfringe%E2%80%9D%20tactics%20into%20tools%20employed%20by%20democratically%20elected%20governments.%20JCBs%20and%20bulldozers%20have%20evolved%20into%20symbols%20of%20instant%20justice.%20Persecution%20through%20non-judicial%20state%20apparatus%20has%20become%20a%20primary%20method.%20Every%20other%20political%20discourse%2C%20particularly%20in%20North%20and%20Northeast%20India%2C%20reinforces%20the%20view%20that%20these%20fringes%20are%20no%20longer%20on%20the%20outskirts%20but%20have%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20become%20part%20of%20the%20mainstream.%20And%20they%20truly%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20are%20they%20also%20the%20majority%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20respond%20to%20it.%20One%2C%20who%20has%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-received-almost-90-of-all-corporate-donations-to-political-parties-in-2022-23%23%3A~%3Atext%3DADR%2527s%2520report%2520also%2520highlighted%2520the%2Cwent%2520to%2520the%2520BJP%2520alone.%5C%22%3Eresources%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Two%2C%20what%20is%20playing%20on%20the%20screens%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20of%20digital%20transformation%2C%20misinformation%20and%20troops%20of%20favourable%20video%20editors%20can%20sway%20voters%20and%20construct%20imagery%20of%20leaders%20and%20parties%20far%20removed%20from%20truth.%20For%20example%2C%20consider%20the%20case%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20the%20two%20primary%20political%20rivals%20who%20happen%20to%20be%20approximately%20in%20the%20same%20age%20group.%20Trump%2C%20at%2077%2C%20and%20Biden%2C%20at%2081%2C%20are%20merely%20four%20years%20apart%20in%20age.%20Yet%20a%20campaign%20spotlighting%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20age%20in%20the%20United%20States%20gains%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2023%2F08%2F29%2Fbiden-trump-2024-age-legal-issues%5C%22%3Etraction%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20a%20similar%20focus%20on%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nbcnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpolitics-news%2Ftrump-vs-biden-two-70-somethings-go-it-over-age-n998926%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CSleepy%20Joe%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20propaganda%20caught%20up%20on%20TikTok%20and%20within%20mainstream%20media%2C%20siding%20with%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20narrative.%20This%20pattern%20parallels%20the%20propaganda%20in%20India%20where%20the%20BJP%20labels%20the%20opposition%20as%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%98pappu%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(incompetent)%20and%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fvideo%2Faisa-mauka-phir-kaha-milega-pm-modi-mocks-congress-chief-in-rajya-sabha-2498752-2024-02-07%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAdvertisement-%2C%2527Aisa%2520mauka%2520phir%2520kaha%2520milega%2527%253A%2520PM%2520Modi%2520mocks%2CCongress%2520chief%2520in%2520Rajya%2520Sabha%26amp%3Btext%3DPrime%2520Minister%2520Narendra%2520Modi%2520on%2CPresident%2527s%2520Address%2520in%2520Rajya%2520Sabha.%5C%22%3Echaracterisation%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20speech%20as%20%E2%80%9Centertaining%E2%80%9D%20is%20followed%20by%20a%20campaign%20on%20prime-time%20TV%2C%20shaping%20the%20debate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Fmedia%2Frepublic-debates-study-shows-channel-promotoes-modi-ndtv%5C%22%3Eagenda%20set%20by%20the%20far%E2%80%93right%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDigital%20competition%20is%20brutal%2C%20unkind%20and%20leaves%20no%20space%20for%20truth%20to%20travel%20faster%20than%20an%20entertaining%20lie.%20If%20anything%2C%20digital%20outlook%20thrives%20on%20it.%20Social%20media%20platforms%20and%20online%20spaces%20provide%20a%20megaphone%20for%20extreme%20views%2C%20amplifying%20their%20impact%20beyond%20their%20numerical%20presence.%20The%20far-right%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20command%20attention%20is%20confused%20with%20broad%20public%20endorsement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20those%20of%20us%20in%20our%20school%2C%20which%20was%20equally%20diverse%20like%20the%20Indian%20demographics%2C%20the%20majority%20electorate%20is%20silent.%20Only%20a%20handful%20of%20individuals%2C%20often%20the%20same%20set%20of%20familiar%20faces%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20vocal%2C%20ringing%20the%20bell%20and%20warning%20us%20about%20the%20challenges%20facing%20our%20democracy.%20The%20silent%20majority%20watches%20far-right%20propaganda%20capturing%20discourse%20but%20sits%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fwhat-explains-the-political-rights-ascendancy-to-global-power%5C%22%3EWhat%20Explains%20the%20Political%20Right%E2%80%99s%20Ascendancy%20to%20Global%20Power%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-far-right%20parties%20misread%20this%20and%20take%20a%20cautious%20approach.%20If%20recent%20election%20results%20(Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20and%20Telangana)%20tell%20us%20anything%2C%20it%20is%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20people%E2%80%9D%20want%20the%20far-right%20BJP%20to%20be%20reined%20in.%20Non-far-right%20parties%20often%20take%20cues%20from%20the%20electoral%20success%20of%20the%20far-right%20and%20overestimate%20people%E2%80%99s%20affinity%20to%20traditional%20values%20or%20a%20sense%20of%20narrow%20nationalism.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20they%20lose%20sight%20of%20the%20silent%20majority%2C%20which%20cares%20about%20democratic%20values%20like%20equality%20and%20wants%20a%20government%20that%20delivers%20on%20public%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20elections%20reveal%20that%20co-opting%20far-right%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20soft%20Hindutva%20%E2%80%93%20projecting%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Van%20Gaman%20Marg%E2%80%99%20as%20an%20achievement%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%20%E2%80%93%20did%20not%20help%20them%20win%20votes.%20If%20anything%2C%20it%20cast%20doubt%20among%20voters%20about%20the%20political%20ideology%20of%20the%20non-far-right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20like%20Kamal%20Nath%20focused%20on%20the%20clamorous%20voices%20of%20the%20far-right%2C%20and%20risked%20neglecting%20more%20tempered%20and%20nuanced%20views%2C%20resulting%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVigneshJourno%2Fstatus%2F1732426232841506924%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Elosses%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fbjp-3-1-assembly-election-results-in-madhya-pradesh-rajasthan-chhattisgarh-telangana-congress-2024-challenges%2Farticle67601613.ece%5C%22%3Eurban%20and%20semi-rural%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Whereas%2C%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20presented%20an%20alternative%20ideological%20agenda%20and%20did%20not%20play%20on%20the%20far-right%E2%80%99s%20turf.%20Evidence%20from%20these%204-state%20elections%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-wave-welfare-schemes-modi-popularity-women-voters-2023-assembly-election-results-analysis%2Farticle67618017.ece%5C%22%3Esuggests%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Congress%20vote%20share%20increased%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVigneshJourno%2Fstatus%2F1732426232841506924%2Fphoto%2F1%5C%22%3Erural%20areas%20across%20all%20four%20states%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20indicates%20an%20electorate%20seeking%20politics%20driven%20by%20issues%20that%20directly%20address%20the%20everyday%20life%20of%20the%20people%2C%20rather%20than%20an%20imaginary%20alternative%20reality%20of%20%E2%80%9CRam%20Rajya%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20silent%20majority%2C%20in%20its%20desire%20for%20a%20modern%20democracy%2C%20adopts%20a%20conservative%20stance%20%E2%80%94%20a%20dichotomy%20and%20anomaly%20in%20itself.%20They%20are%20the%20people%20with%20an%20attitude%20of%20%E2%80%98wait%20and%20watch%E2%80%99.%20They%20observe%20non-far-right%20parties%20adopting%20far-right%20politics%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20electorate%20which%20shows%20a%20disconnect%20with%20their%20past%20stances%2C%20policies%20and%20limited%20ambitions%20for%20future%20reform.%20That%20frustrates%20the%20silent%20majority.%20But%20all%20is%20not%20to%20be%20non-far-right%20parties%E2%80%99%20blame.%20The%20silent%20majority%20is%20also%20impatient%2C%20inconsistent%2C%20indecisive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20non-far-right%20can%20still%20challenge%20the%20far-right.%20The%20strategy%20is%20straightforward%3A%20present%20a%20consistent%20alternative%20ideology%20to%20that%20of%20the%20far-right%2C%20broaden%20the%20alliance%2C%20and%20do%20not%20play%20on%20the%20far-right%E2%80%99s%20turf.%20The%20silent%20majority%20will%20find%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPius%20Fozan%20is%20a%20public%20policy%20student%20at%20Central%20European%20University%20and%20the%20Brandt%20School.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710120641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08152830%2F415251923_1140688907425340_6473205362871466006_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-an-alternative-ideology-is-important-the-far-right-is-loud-not-the-silent-majority%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20times%20of%20digital%20transformation%2C%20misinformation%20and%20troops%20of%20favourable%20video%20editors%20can%20sway%20voters%20and%20construct%20imagery%20of%20leaders%20and%20parties%20far%20removed%20from%20truth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-an-alternative-ideology-is-important-the-far-right-is-loud-not-the-silent-majority%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Serum%20looks%20beyond%20Covid%20with%20new%20vaccines%20for%20malaria%2C%20dengue%3A%20CEO%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710120333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F13%2Ffull%2F1681361855-4772.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fserum-looks-beyond-covid-with-new-vaccines-for-malaria-dengue-ceo-124031000692_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Serum%20produces%20AstraZeneca's%20Covid-19%20vaccine%20under%20the%20brand%20name%20Covishield%20in%20India%2C%20and%20also%20makes%20Novavax's%20protein-based%20Covid%20shots%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%