India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20will%20take%20place%20over%20a%20time%20period%20of%2015%20years%2C%20during%20which%20the%20creation%20of%20about%20ten%20lakh%20jobs%20will%20be%20facilitated%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Findia-efta-trade-agreement-100-billion-deal-9205865%2F%5C%22%3EUnion%20commerce%20minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20said%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndian%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EExpress%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20investment%20will%20come%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-03-10%2Findia-efta-bloc-sign-free-trade-pact-after-16-years-in-making%5C%22%3Emostly%20from%20the%20private%20sector%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bloomberg%20cited%20Goyal%20as%20saying.%20The%20news%20agency%20previously%20reported%20that%20it%20would%20likely%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-02-07%2Findia-eyes-100-billion-investment-deal-with-switzerland-norway%5C%22%3Etargeted%20at%20manufacturing%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20deal%2C%20EFTA%20countries%20will%20face%20reduced%20tariffs%20for%20processed%20foods%20and%20beverages%20as%20well%20as%20for%20electrical%20machinery.%20Their%20pharmaceutical%20and%20medical%20devices%20industries%20will%20also%20benefit%2C%20Bloomberg%E2%80%99s%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20the%20deal%20will%20liberalise%20access%20for%20Indian%20products%20such%20as%20rice%20and%20will%20facilitate%20the%20smoother%20movement%20of%20Indian%20professionals%20into%20the%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20exporting%20farm%20produce%20to%20Switzerland%20may%20remain%20difficult%20due%20to%20tariffs%2C%20quality%20standards%20and%20approval%20requirements%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fkey-details-indias-pact-with-four-nation-european-trade-bloc-2024-03-10%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%20citing%20analysts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwitzerland%20will%20benefit%20from%20reductions%20of%20high%20tariffs%20on%20around%2095%25%20of%20industrial%20goods%20it%20exports%20to%20India%20%E2%80%93%20excluding%20gold%20%E2%80%93%20either%20immediately%20or%20in%20a%20phased%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoods%20from%20the%20country%20that%20are%20slated%20to%20become%20cheaper%20in%20India%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Fforeign-trade%2Findia-efta-trade-deal-swiss-watches-chocolates-to-enter-indian-market-at-lower-prices%2Farticleshow%2F108369011.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ehigh-end%20watches%20and%20chocolates%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorway%E2%80%99s%20industries%20minister%20Jan%20Christian%20Vestre%20said%20that%20while%20companies%20from%20his%20country%20currently%20face%20up%20to%2040%25%20import%20taxes%20on%20certain%20goods%2C%20the%20trade%20deal%20secures%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia-says-europe-trade-group-commits-100-bln-15-year-deal-2024-03-10%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cnil%20import%20taxes%20on%20nearly%20every%20Norwegian%20good%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Reuters%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20five%20countries%20have%20to%20ratify%20the%20deal%20before%20it%20takes%20effect.%20According%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20Switzerland%E2%80%99s%20government%20said%20it%20will%20begin%20this%20process%20immediately%20so%20that%20the%20deal%20can%20be%20approved%20by%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20EFTA%E2%80%99s%20fifth-largest%20trading%20partner%20and%20two-way%20trade%20between%20the%20two%20amounted%20to%20%2425%20billion%20according%20to%20calculations%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20comes%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20has%20emphasised%20high%20GDP%20growth%20over%20the%20last%20quarter%20and%20the%20Union%20government%20says%20it%20aims%20to%20achieve%20annual%20exports%20of%20%241%20trillion%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Findia-europes-efta-bloc-sign-100-billion-deal%2Fa-68485259%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710081659000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10200722%2FIndia-efta-II-n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findia-efta-free-trade-pact-10-billion-investment-lowered-tariffs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20deal%2C%20signed%20between%20India%20and%20the%20four-country%20European%20Free-Trade%20Association%2C%20provides%20for%20reduces%20tariffs%20for%20goods%20that%20the%20bloc's%20members%20export%20to%20India%20as%20well%20as%20for%20liberalised%20access%20for%20certain%20Indian%20goods%20to%20the%20markets%20of%20those%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findia-efta-free-trade-pact-10-billion-investment-lowered-tariffs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Bank%20appoints%20Brajesh%20Kumar%20Singh%20as%20executive%20director%20for%203%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710081035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F23%2Ffull%2F1700736502-1837.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Findian-bank-appoints-brajesh-kumar-singh-as-executive-director-for-3-years-124031000453_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prior%20taking%20up%20the%20new%20responsibility%2C%20Singh%20was%20serving%20Bank%20of%20Baroda%20as%20its%20Chief%20General%20Manager%20-%20Human%20Resources%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2