%20and%20Indira%20Colony%20with%20skills%20for%20life%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Feducating-underprivileged-kids-5-1709817818.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Feducating-underprivileged-kids-5-1709817818-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Feducating-underprivileged-kids-5-1709817818-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Feducating-underprivileged-kids-5-1709817818-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Feducating-underprivileged-kids-5-1709817818-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344236%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENayi%20Disha%20equips%20children%20from%20the%20Harijan%20Colony%20and%20Indira%20Colony%20with%20skills%20for%20life%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Seema%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20kids%E2%80%99%20lives%20in%20real-time%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20effect%20of%20time%20is%20evident%20in%20the%20dreams%20of%20Nayi%20Disha.%20What%20started%20as%20a%20handful%20of%20kids%20being%20taught%20English%20in%20a%20small%20room%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20now%20scaled%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335548%2Fthis-hero-turned-mud-walls-into-blackboards-streets-into-schools-for-10000-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%20100%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20spread%20across%20eight%20rooms%20learning%20a%20variety%20of%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20mathematics%2C%20environmental%20science%2C%20art%2C%20computers%20and%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20astounding%20than%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20participation%20has%20been%20the%20support%20of%20the%20parents%2C%20notes%20Seema.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20have%20begun%20to%20see%20an%20improvement%20in%20their%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20realisation%20deepened%20during%20the%20lockdown%20that%20ensued%20amid%20the%20COVID%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20of%20online%20classes%2C%20it%20so%20happened%20that%20parents%20were%20at%20home%20while%20the%20kids%20were%20learning.%20We%20would%20send%20them%20activities%20and%20worksheets%20to%20solve.%20The%20parents%20ended%20up%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334571%2Fkalpit-veerwal-jee-main-topper-launches-education-startup-iit-bombay-placement-package%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elearning%20a%20lot%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20bargain%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20chuckles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20lockdown%2C%20the%20entire%20%3Cem%3Ebasti%3C%2Fem%3E%20knew%20the%20days%20of%20the%20week%2C%20months%20of%20the%20year%2C%20and%20multiplication%20tables%20on%20the%20tips%20of%20their%20fingers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20parents%20got%20to%20see%20how%20much%20value%20we%20are%20adding%20to%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20lives.%20They%20realised%20that%20their%20children%20actually%20study%20at%20Nayi%20Disha%20and%20that%20there%20are%20people%20who%20are%20spending%20dedicated%20time%20with%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20in%20mindset%20is%20refreshing.%20The%20parents%E2%80%99%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334155%2Fbengaluru-ngo-dream-a-dream-educates-underprivileged-children-life-skills-happiness-curriculum-delhi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eview%20of%20the%20NGO%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20space%20of%20learning%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20seeing%20it%20as%20a%20creche%2C%20is%20a%20win%20according%20to%20Seema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchool%20is%20freedom%20for%20these%20children.%20Right%20from%20the%209%20am%20assembly%20and%20the%20circle%20time%20%E2%80%94%20where%20they%20share%20their%20observations%20about%20the%20weather%2C%20talk%20about%20their%20day%20and%20express%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20chatter%20at%20the%20mid-day%20meal%20distribution%20and%20English%20classes%20that%20are%20conducted%20by%20volunteer%20students%20from%20colleges%20across%20Gurugram%2C%20each%20moment%20is%20a%20celebration%20of%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20kids%20love%20theatre%20sessions%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20makes%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333542%2Fupsc-cse-interview-round-tips-by-ias-officers-personality-test-toppers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfident%20and%20outgoing%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20encourages%20them%20to%20speak%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20great%20because%20we%20noticed%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20are%20shy%20and%20reluctant%20to%20speak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20at%201.30%20pm%20when%20the%20kids%20file%20to%20go%20back%20home%2C%20brighter%20than%20the%20smile%20on%20any%20of%20their%20faces%2C%20is%20the%20one%20on%20their%20teacher%E2%80%99s%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENisha%2C%20who%20has%20been%20with%20Nayi%20Disha%20since%20it%20started%2C%20is%20Seema%E2%80%99s%20rock.%20%E2%80%9CSeema%20ma%E2%80%99am%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20teacher%20and%20someone%20put%20me%20in%20touch%20with%20her.%20Since%20the%20start%2C%20I%20have%20been%20teaching%20these%20children%20many%20subjects%20and%20have%20watched%20these%20children%20grow.%20I%20remember%20them%20being%20unruly%2C%20but%20with%20time%2C%20we%20taught%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332617%2Fias-officers-share-revision-tips-tricks-techniques-upsc-cse-aspirants%2F%5C%22%