of%20the%20Brown%20Bear%20(%3Cem%3EUrsus%20arctos%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20the%20Himalayan%20Brown%20Bear%20is%20largely%20confined%20to%20rolling%20uplands%2C%20alpine%2C%20subalpine%2C%20glacial%20moraines%20and%20barren%20regions%20of%20the%20Greater%20Himalayas%20and%20some%20parts%20of%20Trans-Himalayas%E2%80%A6%5BIn%20India%5D%20They%20are%20predominantly%20found%20in%20the%20Kargil%20region%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20where%20their%20distribution%20is%20fragmentary%2C%20spread%20across%20Drass%2C%20Suru%20valley%2C%20Shargole%2C%20and%20Zanskar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201237px)%20100vw%2C%201237px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221237%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brown%20Bear%20and%20Snow%20Leopards%20in%20Ladakh%20taken%20by%20a%20Photographer%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582.jpeg%201237w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582-300x187.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582-500x312.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582-768x480.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FKaramjeetSingh-1-1709561582-150x94.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343884%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22773%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20people%20at%20Roots%20Ladakh%2C%20Karamjeet%20feels%20that%20he%20owes%20his%20development%20as%20a%20wildlife%20photographer%20to%20Zaheer%20Bagh%2C%20a%20local%20hotelier%20and%20wildlife%20enthusiast%20in%20Kargil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHis%20unwavering%20support%20and%20shared%20passion%20for%20exploration%20ha