tracts%20rare%20earth%20metals%2C%20such%20as%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%20and%20manganese%20from%20used%20Li-ion%20cells%2C%20which%20are%20then%20bought%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20industries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20EVs%2C%20pharmaceuticals%2C%20electroplating%20and%20fertiliser.%20But%20if%20these%20used%20cells%20have%20some%20charge%20left%2C%20they%20repurpose%20them%20into%20batteries%20for%20off-grid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256764%2Fmumbai-startup-electric-vehicle-features-charger-cost-install-magenta-street-light-ev-charging-solutions-solar-energy-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20EV%20chargers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20inverters%2C%20or%20other%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20developed%20an%20innovative%20procedure%20for%20recycling%20various%20batteries%2C%20employing%20specialised%20techniques%20and%20advanced%20hydrometallurgical%20processes.%20As%20a%20major%20supplier%20of%20sustainable%20battery%20solutions%20in%20India%2C%20they%20have%20even%20secured%20a%20patent%20for%20their%20Zero%20Waste-Zero%20Emission%20Technology%20and%20successfully%20recycled%20about%20220%20million%20batteries%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201137px)%20100vw%2C%201137px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-2-1709299204.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221137%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Recycling%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%20is%20good%20for%20the%20environment%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-2-1709299204.jpg%201137w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-2-1709299204-300x201.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-2-1709299204-500x335.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-2-1709299204-768x515.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-2-1709299204-150x101.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343655%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22762%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBatX%20Energies%20is%20an%20R%26amp%3BD%20driven%20venture%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20recycle%20and%20repurpose%20used%20Li-ion%20batteries%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20begins%20with%20sourcing%20used%20Li-ion%20batteries%20from%20formal%20entities%20like%20EV%20manufacturers%20and%20ventures%20engaged%20in%20building%20stationary%20applications%20like%20telecom%20towers%20where%20these%20batteries%20are%20deployed%2C%20power%20electronics%2C%20and%20other%20electronic%20devices%20like%20laptops%2C%20mobile%20phones%2C%20etc.%20They%20also%20source%20these%20batteries%20from%20the%20informal%20sector%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20about%2080%25%20of%20the%20sourcing%20of%20battery%20cells%20comes%20from%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20because%20a%20majority%20of%20them%20are%20extracted%20from%20mobile%20phones%20and%20laptops.%20However%2C%20our%20market%20research%20suggests%20that%20the%20organised%20sector%20will%20soon%20overtake%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sourcing%20these%20used%20batteries.%20Unlike%20laptop%20or%20phone%20batteries%2C%20EV%20batteries%20cannot%20be%20left%20in%20the%20unorganised%20sector.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20capacity%20or%20capability%20to%20handle%20them.%20One%20tonne%20of%20Li-ion%20battery%20waste%20is%20equivalent%20to%201%20e-bus%20battery%3B%203%20EV%20car%20batteries%3B%2029%20three-wheeler%20batteries%3B%2040%20two-wheeler%20batteries%3B%20or%2022%2C000%20mobile%20phone%20batteries%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20sourced%2C%20yo