https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F306265%2Fengineer-covers-long-distance-journey-in-electric-vehicle-sushil-reddy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMG%20Motor%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20even%20developed%20home%20inverters%20employing%20second-life%20EV%20batteries%20at%20the%20same%20cost%20as%20a%20lead-acid%20inverter%2C%20which%20is%20hazardous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20developed%20a%20small%20unit%20which%20can%20run%20for%20five%20years.%20We%20are%20going%20to%20deploy%20these%20inverters%20soon%20in%20rural%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Once%20these%20second-life%20batteries%20come%20to%20the%20end%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20we%20will%20take%20them%20back%20and%20recycle%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Utkarsh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There's%20a%20lot%20of%20value%20in%20recycling%20in%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-Energies-Operations-2-1709299355-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343658%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWorking%20at%20the%20BatX%20Energies%20facility%20where%20they%20recycle%20used%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20batteries%20are%20deemed%20not%20fit%20for%20second-life%20applications%2C%20they%20are%20dismantled%2C%20discharged%2C%20and%20crushed%20into%20powder%20at%20their%20facility%20in%20Sikandrabad%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20They%20call%20this%20crushed%20powder%20%E2%80%98black%20mass%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20then%20transported%20to%20their%20main%20chemical%20recycling%20facility%2C%20and%20here%2C%20they%20extract%20materials%20like%20lithium%2C%20cobalt%2C%20nickel%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20black%20mass%2C%20all%20battery%20grade%20material%20including%20graphite%20is%20removed%2C%20and%20then%20impurities%20like%20aluminium%2C%20copper%20and%20cake.%20After%20this%2C%20we%20extract%20lithium%2C%20nickel%20and%20cobalt.%20Once%20we%20extract%20these%20materials%2C%20we%20sell%20them%20to%20material%20refiners%20who%20use%20them%20to%20make%20new%20Li-ion%20cells.%20But%20materials%20like%20lithium%20are%20also%20used%20in%20the%20pharmaceutical%20industry%20to%20make%20anti-depression%20medication%2C%20etc.%20Cobalt%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20is%20used%20in%20the%20ceramic%20and%20pain%20industry%20while%20Nickel%20is%20employed%20in%20electroplating%20and%20the%20fertiliser%20industry%20as%20well.%20We%20only%20produce%20high-grade%20material%20(99.6%25%20purity)%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Utkarsh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikrant%20goes%20on%20to%20claim%20that%20the%20process%20they%20have%20developed%20to%20repurpose%20or%20recycle%20these%20old%20batteries%20is%20chemistry-agnostic%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20they%20are%20lithium%20iron%20phosphate%20(LFP)%20batteries%2C%20lithium%20nickel%20manganese%20cobalt%20(NMC)%20batteries%2C%20Li-ion%20batteries%2C%20or%20lead%20acid%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20took%20us%20five%20years%20to%20design%20and%20develop%20this%20process%20we%20have%20established.%20We%20currently%20have%20a%20patent%20on%20our%20%E2%80%98Waste%20to%20Zero%20Emission%20Technology%E2%80%99.%20The%20patent%20is%20on%20their%20apparatus%2C%20methods%20and%20process.%20Since%20we%20initially%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20funds%2C%20we%20developed%20the%20recycling%20plant%20ourselves.%20We%20have%20not%20imported%20any%20of%20the%20machinery%20in%20our%20production%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20near%20future%2C%20however%2C%20BatX%20will%20look%20to%20alter%20their%20operations%20based%20on%20a%20hub%20and%20spoke%20model.%20Although%20their%20main%20centre%20of%20operations%20lies%20in%20Sikandrabad%2C%20UP%20(Hub)%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20set%20up%20different%20facilities%20(spokes)%20in%20places%20like%20Hosur%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Siliguri%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%20Why%20are%20they%20adopting%20this%20new%20operating%20model%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20say%2C%20we%20collect%20old%20Li-ion%20batteries%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336276%2Fmadhura-rajvanshi-fulbright-scholar-distinguished-award-phaltan-rural-maharashtra%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebut%20want%20to%20transport%20them%20to%20our%20hub%20in%20UP.%20Despite%20all%20the%20safety%20measures%20we%20take%2C%20there%20is%20some%20risk%20involved%20in%20transporting%20them.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20are%20planning%20to%20create%20facilities%20(spokes)%20in%20states%20like%20Gujarat%20(and%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Karnataka)%20so%20that%20we%20can%20transport%20our%20old%20batteries%20from%20Maharashtra%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Extracting%20key%20materials%20while%20recycling%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FBatX-5-1709299437-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343660%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EExtracting%20key%20materials%20while%20recycling%20Lithium-ion%20batteries%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFunding%20and%20looking%20ahead%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%20December%202023%2C%20BatX%20Energies%20raised%20USD%205%20million%20in%20pre-Series%20A%20funding.%20The%20round%20was%20led%20by%20investors%2C%20such%20as%20Zephyr%20Peacock%2C%20but%20also%20saw%20participation%20from%20investment%20platforms%20like%20Lets%20Venture%20and%20existing%20investors%20like%20JITO%20Angel%20Network%2C%20and%20family%20offices%20of%20Mankind%20Pharma%2C%20Excel%20Industries%2C%20and%20BluSmart%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20press%20release%20they%20issued%2C%20Pankaj%20Raina%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Zephyr%20Peacock%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20company%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20a%20crucial%20stakeholder%20in%20the%20battery%20supply%20chain%20in%20India%2C%20as%20recyclers%20will%20be%20a%20significant%20source%20of%20critical%20materials%20for%20Li-ion%20battery%20manufacturing.%20We%20are%20excited%20to%20partner%20with%20them%20on%20this%20journey.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-